[b]TVO - Big Ideas, January 14 2012: David Brooks on 'The Social Animal'[/b]

In a lecture entitled How Success Happens, New York Times columnist and author, David Brooks, draws from the research in his latest book [i]The Social Animal: The Hidden Sources of Love, Character and Achievement[/i].  His lecture was delivered at the Rotman School of Management, University of Toronto.

